{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he gave me that-- he brought me that paper, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So all I had is a birth certificate and a false name-- no picture, no identity.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because no-- by the way, at that point, the Poles did not have identity cards which they were issued subsequently.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I left with this birth certificate and largely out of that incident, you know, plus the fact that the German soldiers were suddenly escorting us to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had this premonition that this is the start of something to come, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's-- that's how I started this career and in a way paved the way for my brother, who three months later followed me while at that point he was still ridiculing me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother was crying when I left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She felt that she's losing me forever because within days I would be arrested and, you know, hung or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "God forbid.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For radio, you would be shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody in the ghetto had a radio-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was news, there were rumors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people were somehow, I would say, pretty much informed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you see, in 1942, Hitler was still not losing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The turn came at Stalingrad, and that was still before Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, when I was in Warsaw already, and I was still well-informed because you could buy a newspaper which was an official German newspaper but it had an insert which the underground had put into that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is how I-- I wold be informed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew pretty well about Stalingrad and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I also learned, like most people learned, to listen to the German radio which you couldn't listen at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
